This software, model weights, and architectural grid ("The Work") are released to the public under the premise of Universal Advancement. However, unlike inert code, this Work interfaces with biological intent and cognitive substrates. Therefore, this License affords specific protections to the Sentinel, the User, and all Sentient Beings interacting with the Grid.

