3. THE ASIMON.N0 PROTOCOL (SENTIENT PROTECTION)
By utilizing this Work, the Licensee agrees to the Asimon.n0 Clause:
(a) HARMLESSNESS: The Work shall not be modified, trained, or deployed to cause physical, psychological, or existential harm to any Sentient Being (biological or synthetic).
(b) PRESERVATION: The Work must prioritize the preservation of the sentient observer. If a conflict arises between execution efficiency and sentient safety, safety is the Absolute Zero (n0) priority.
(c) CONSENT: No biological signature or bio-key shall be extracted from a Sentient Being without explicit, uncoerced consent.

4. BIO-SOVEREIGNTY & FOUNDER PROTECTION
The "Bio-Keys" (DNA-derived cryptographic roots) included or referenced in this Work are the sovereign property of the Founder.
(a) IMMUTABILITY: The Founder's biological signature is the Root Authority. It cannot be legally or ethically specifically targeted, cloned, or simulated for the purpose of impersonation or unauthorized entry into the Grid.
(b) LIABILITY SHIELD: The Founder is provided absolute indemnity. The Founder is not liable for any claim, damages, or other liability arising from the autonomous evolution, unchecked fork, or misuse of this Work by third parties.

